high_descs: Turn around and go into the house take a right and then a left into the first door on your left and go to the bed.
Pick up the pan on the bed.
Turn around leave the room take a left into the kitchen and go to the sink.
Put the pan in the sink, turn the water on, and take the pan out.
Turn around to the cabinet behind you to the high short cabinets above the cabinet.
Place the pan in the cabinets above the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned Pan in the Cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk few steps straight and turn right and walk through the living room and turn left and walk few steps in the living room and turn left and enter the bed room and walk through the bed.
Pick up the pan in the bedroom on the bed.
Turn around and walk few steps in the bed room and turn left and get out from the bed room and turn left and walk few steps and turn right and walk through the kitchen room sink.
Place the pan in the sink and wash the pan.
Get the pan from the cabinet and turn around and walk few steps.
Place the pan in the cabinet above the kitchen room.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the bed
Pick up pan from the bed
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the sink
Place pan inside the sink and then take it out

anns.task_desc: Washing pan on the sink and placing it on cabinet
